    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>這是我的第一個blog, 對於為什麼選擇<a href="http://hexo.io" target="_blank" rel="external">hexo</a>做我的blog呢？<br>因為這可是nodejs + markdown 所組成的blog！！<br>是不是很潮呀~!<br>廢話不多說趕快看如何啟動吧<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="快速啟動">快速啟動</h2>
<p>首先安裝 nvm + nodejs (ubuntu) :</p>
<h3 id="nvm">nvm</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>$ curl https://raw.github.com/creationix/nvm/v0.<span class="number">4.0</span>/install.sh | sh
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>新增以下命令列到 <code>.bashrc</code> 的最後:</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
4
5
6
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="comment"># set PATH so it includes user's private bin if it exists</span>
<span class="keyword">if</span> [ <span class="operator">-d</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.nvm/bin"</span> ] ; <span class="keyword">then</span>
  <span class="keyword">export</span> PATH=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.nvm/bin:<span class="variable">$PATH</span>"</span>
  <span class="keyword">export</span> NVM_DIR=<span class="string">"<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.nvm"</span>
<span class="keyword">fi</span>
[ <span class="operator">-s</span> <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.nvm/nvm.sh"</span> ] && . <span class="string">"<span class="variable">$HOME</span>/.nvm/nvm.sh"</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="nodejs">nodejs</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>$ nvm install v0.<span class="number">10.26</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>接著安裝hexo:</p>
<h3 id="hexo">hexo</h3>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>$ npm install -g hexo
</pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>接著只需要幾個簡單的命令, 你就可以打理好一切</p>
<p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre>1
2
3
4
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre>$ hexo init      <span class="comment">#初始化</span>
$ hexo n <span class="string">'title'</span> <span class="comment">#寫名為'title'的文章</span>
$ hexo g         <span class="comment">#生成</span>
$ hexo s         <span class="comment">#啟動, 預設為port:4000</span>
</pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>真的超簡單的吧！</p>
]]></content>
